{"tid":1466732,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【跪求大家入黎睇下，我好想香港贏】關於鬼關於衝動","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:53:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T19:53:55.000Z","uid":109820,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"63f651ff7cf2dbbb2ec265951424864459278fdd","tid":1466732,"uid":109820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:53:30.000Z","msg":"大家要認清一樣野<br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>我方陣營一定有鬼</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>亦一定有好激動嘅人</strong></span><br />\n唔係個個都可以<ins>完全冷靜完全理性</ins><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">失去理性係人之常情</span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以之後要做咩都好，一定要考慮定<strong>呢兩個情況</strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有鬼你會點？</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你見到有人失去理性會點？</span></span></strong><br />\n你要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">問清楚自己</span><br />\n呢場抗爭<strong>無大台</strong>，唔好旨意有人教你幾時做啲咩。<br />\n<br />\n我會話，<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">堅持、不割蓆係唯一真理。</span></span></ins></strong>"},{"pid":"eda6d7a26dac7c8e10bfecd2dd3d7ce60c83d978","tid":1466732,"uid":109820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:54:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7f32bf90039c647849f5e5efbddaad8fbbb6f30a","tid":1466732,"uid":109820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:10:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ba21ee5baf5b3a86c48e1347ecbdde1031470fb5","tid":1466732,"uid":259579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:11:25.000Z","msg":"啱呀"},{"pid":"34819e8648fd2dabb6565950a14fe48ab21c85d8","tid":1466732,"uid":95487,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:13:42.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有<br />\n唔會捉得晒<br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5f37dc4f24c7cc54814d3fa310d31a0ddbcb7b9","tid":1466732,"uid":109820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:14:25.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"585a04ae35a2534b1cfb65d24a688d694d6b0820","tid":1466732,"uid":5205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:16:23.000Z","msg":"必須保護100%和理非行動 <br />\n<br />\n我地可以提早決定100%和理非定 有後續 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警察風向 破壞連登 咩淪陷 唔好信<br />\n<br />\n信左就中警察計<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n和理非 取消黑衫行動 勇武就無左保護 鬼亦無咁多機會滲透<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一定要支持 勇武就無左保護 自然要勇武休息下<br />\n咁鬼既滲透亦無左機會。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係 講到明有下場既就全民黑衫 （例如免費過海之類）<br />\n<br />\n機場只宣傳 同控制人流 有人搞事就 比泛民 等泛民開記者會<br />\n<br />\n幫手講佢係鬼 <br />\n<br />\n另外唔建議帶口罩 和理非活動係要一家大細都可以參與"},{"pid":"677a89c4f045e36924c7c580ddf19d735d5c8c3a","tid":1466732,"uid":109820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:18:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"047def8e66fac4336b35c4a4a6af025394f007aa","tid":1466732,"uid":285539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:18:31.000Z","msg":"我同意唔割蓆，但如果佢真係想放核彈我一定會阻止佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />遇到類似嘅事我諗大家唔應該放任甚至支持囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"047b88c8e61bec3e08b86819e06b7e7ecec500c8","tid":1466732,"uid":280899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:19:40.000Z","msg":"係室飽機場    係包和機場   唔係佔領機場      唔係癱瘓機場<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1466104\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1466104</a>"},{"pid":"4f92cc3f0733cc6d591150e42187b8511438ecff","tid":1466732,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:26:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cd92baf4565b62e3fe504fc45438306966595958","tid":1466732,"uid":241458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:32:45.000Z","msg":"聽日停止捉鬼，和理非式舉牌話今晚單嘢係衝動咗，低低地摜一鋪，坐返喺接機大堂，沖淡返今日啲嘢先"},{"pid":"c6133b55578765fcf4a1e6d0715019c9f7f27d88","tid":1466732,"uid":180362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:33:40.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"171bf8af757a0b998aeff1ebeb6a5287c0603afe","tid":1466732,"uid":217306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:34:33.000Z","msg":"冇錯<br />\n我都真係好想香港贏<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n核爆都唔割席，和理非食屎啦！我有三個建議，跪喺度求大家睇咗佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1467719\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1467719</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ce8514e49bfdfa0b653c43edd96ff80d9502bf29","tid":1466732,"uid":245680,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:38:11.000Z","msg":"點樣都唔會割，勇武我問心做唔到，但係一定會係後面支援義士們"},{"pid":"8d45bb1c901de0e6afed08c5690aca4a1b14c317","tid":1466732,"uid":142338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:46:05.000Z","msg":"要鬧就鬧共產黨，對準個政權，唔好再互屌同路人！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1467720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1467720</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c7c634043d71729c0c75c3c53695400e6eb69559","tid":1466732,"uid":290176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"047def8e66fac4336b35c4a4a6af025394f007aa","tid":1466732,"uid":285539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:18:31.000Z","msg":"我同意唔割蓆，但如果佢真係想放核彈我一定會阻止佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />遇到類似嘅事我諗大家唔應該放任甚至支持囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:48:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd33ef979099bf568d08e3e822eb0e9ea14db6eb","tid":1466732,"uid":109820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:49:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f1bf1cef65ccb1a56a15caab4d5468afdfae28ea","tid":1466732,"uid":142338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:51:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"337c7fcd60cd4fbf8f5e766a095299ac979bd2b2","tid":1466732,"uid":238197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:00:30.000Z","msg":"［事後檢討］今日捉鬼事件<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1467998\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1467998</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG <br />\n<br />\n推<br />\n同意大家好情緒化<br />\n唔代表今日輸今日錯<br />\n我地係不斷進步"},{"pid":"3bcadbab861d39d0e96493236fb6b041fa6071ab","tid":1466732,"uid":296350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:05:46.000Z","msg":"不割席 不分化 兄弟爬山<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">弱點已經比敵人對準！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n只要搵幾條仆街帶風就已經成功破解我哋呢三句格言！！<br />\n<br />\n不割不分吖嘛！！<br />\n搵人帶風自然有人跟！！<br />\n搵鬼落場做乜嘢都可以入你數！<br />\n<br />\n再唔諗辦法<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">捉鬼</span></strong>，我哋真係死撚硬！！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">兄弟不割，鬼同分化撚一定要割</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n要有效捉鬼，前線一定要<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">有底線共識</span></strong>，咩可以做，咩唔可以做，一過底線就係鬼，即捉！唔係割席，唔係分化呀！係要<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">認真解決問題呀！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n分化同鬼從來都係狗共致勝之道<br />\n，要對付唯一方法就係<strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">團結</span></strong></strong>！！<br />\n既然團結，就嘗試傾個底線共識，唔係所有野要有共識，底線真係有須要呀！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">一定捉鬼呀！！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">底線共識大家可以討論</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大前提係畀全世界知我哋係<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">為自由良知而戰嘅正義之師，係保護市民嘅黑衣人！！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n1.可以打遊擊同快閃， 唔放火/唔掉磚/唔衝/唔主動出手/唔傷及無無辜。<br />\n<br />\n2. 可以佔路set路障，圍，口撩，還拖！但不主動出擊，不傷及無辜。<br />\n<br />\n3.不送頭，所有可以被聯上暴動同暴徒嘅，都唔好做。<br />\n<br />\n4. 贏輿論同民心唔係講緊連登呀！自high有乜撚嘢用！<br />\n<br />\n輿論係正常媒體包括 social media 同埋國際輿論，民心唔使講啦！<br />\n<br />\n失民心同輿論，話撚知你連登幾high幾高漲，大家可以返屋企含撚啦！<br />\n<br />\n輿論同民心係要嚟令對家喺國際/同社會有壓力！<br />\n<br />\n只要set到個底線嘅共識， <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">我哋先可以真正團結，<strong><strong></strong></strong>先有機會贏</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n咁我先真正做到<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">兄弟爬山 不割席 不分化！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n咁多位手足認真諗諗啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"340e60bc512acec5eb111c0a191459ca5c28dc9d","tid":1466732,"uid":259532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:10:09.000Z","msg":"真係對場運動認真的話，就要係最憤怒既時候保持/訓練自己冷靜！！"},{"pid":"c610004fb1ed49d4bfb9f27fc99c1a9e8f2db3c9","tid":1466732,"uid":109820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:11:21.000Z","msg":"大家幫手推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23c3fb2d101d16192ac25625fa26835aba556e3d","tid":1466732,"uid":234352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:16:18.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n求下大家幫我推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n與其諗塞機場對錯，不如諗8.16㩒錢經濟戰<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1467538\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1467538</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"67cb7c6f8ba935fa9464e646e40c333b382c25dc","tid":1466732,"uid":274180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:50:12.000Z","msg":"不分化不割席 只檢討與改進 我要贏啊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468585\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468585</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}